In [10]:
Data1 = Composition_Data.fillna(Composition_Data.mean())
In [11]:
### Bogue method for calculation the percentage of four major compounds
Data1['C3S'] = 4.07*Data1['CaO Cement'] - 7.6*Data1['SiO2 Cement'] - 6.72*Data1['Al2O3 Cement'] - 1.43*Data1['Fe2O Cement'] - 2.85*Data1['SO3 Cement']
Data1['C2S'] = 2.87*Data1['SiO2 Cement'] - 0.754*(3*Data1['CaO Cement']*Data1['SiO2 Cement'])
Data1['C3A'] = 2.65*Data1['Al2O3 Cement'] - 1.69*Data1['Fe2O Cement']
Data1['C4AF'] = 3.04*Data1['Fe2O Cement']
In [12]:
Data1 = Data1.drop(columns= ['SiO2 Cement','CaO Cement','Al2O3 Cement','Fe2O Cement','SO3 Cement'])
